{
  "video_id": "dOt4NkcmIUg",
  "title": "How China is changing the future of shopping | Angela Wang",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12560.0,
      "end_time": 14520.0,
      "text": "This is my nephew,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15280.0,
      "end_time": 16576.0,
      "text": "Yuan Yuan."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 16600.0,
      "end_time": 18960.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s five years old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 18120.0,
      "end_time": 19400.0,
      "text": "super adorable."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 20360.0,
      "end_time": 22336.0,
      "text": "I asked him the other day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 22360.0,
      "end_time": 24720.0,
      "text": "\"What would you like for your birthday this year?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 25360.0,
      "end_time": 29439.0,
      "text": "He said, \"I want to have a one-way mirror Spider-Man mask.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 30000.0,
      "end_time": 32775.0,
      "text": "I had absolutely no idea what he was talking about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 32800.0,
      "end_time": 34775.0,
      "text": "so I said, \"Wow, that&#39;s really cool,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 34800.0,
      "end_time": 36372.0,
      "text": "but how are you going to get it?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 37120.0,
      "end_time": 40160.0,
      "text": "He told me, without a blink of his eyes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 40400.0,
      "end_time": 44119.0,
      "text": "\"I&#39;m going to tell my mom and make a wish before I go to bed."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 44759.0,
      "end_time": 46720.0,
      "text": "My mom will go to shake her mobile phone."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 47400.0,
      "end_time": 51680.0,
      "text": "The next morning, the delivery uncle will give it to me when I wake up.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 53320.0,
      "end_time": 55296.0,
      "text": "I was about to tease him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 55320.0,
      "end_time": 57960.0,
      "text": "but suddenly I realized"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 57120.0,
      "end_time": 59455.0,
      "text": "he was simply telling me the truth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 59480.0,
      "end_time": 63616.0,
      "text": "the truth of what shopping looks like for this generation."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 63640.0,
      "end_time": 67256.0,
      "text": "If you think of it, for a child like Yuan Yuan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 67280.0,
      "end_time": 69576.0,
      "text": "shopping is a very different idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 69600.0,
      "end_time": 72496.0,
      "text": "compared to what my generation had in mind."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 72520.0,
      "end_time": 74776.0,
      "text": "Shopping is always done on mobile,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 74800.0,
      "end_time": 76878.0,
      "text": "and payment is all virtual."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 78000.0,
      "end_time": 82480.0,
      "text": "A huge shopping revolution is happening in China right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 83120.0,
      "end_time": 86976.0,
      "text": "Shopping behaviors, and also technology platforms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 87000.0,
      "end_time": 89856.0,
      "text": "have evolved differently than elsewhere in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 89880.0,
      "end_time": 93776.0,
      "text": "For instance, e-commerce in China is soaring."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 93800.0,
      "end_time": 96616.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s been growing at twice the speed of the United States"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 96640.0,
      "end_time": 99280.0,
      "text": "and a lot of the growth is coming from mobile."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 99920.0,
      "end_time": 104696.0,
      "text": "Every month, 500 million consumers"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 104720.0,
      "end_time": 106816.0,
      "text": "are buying on mobile phones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 106840.0,
      "end_time": 108576.0,
      "text": "and to put that into context,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 108600.0,
      "end_time": 111815.0,
      "text": "that is a total population of the United States,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 111840.0,
      "end_time": 114280.0,
      "text": "UK and Germany combined."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 115400.0,
      "end_time": 118896.0,
      "text": "But it is not just about the scale of the e-commerce,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 118920.0,
      "end_time": 123496.0,
      "text": "it is the speed of adoption and the aggregation of the ecosystems."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 123520.0,
      "end_time": 128150.0,
      "text": "It took China less than five years to become a country of mobile commerce,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 128389.99999999999,
      "end_time": 133176.0,
      "text": "and that is largely because of the two technology platforms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 133200.0,
      "end_time": 134720.0,
      "text": "Alibaba and Tencent."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 135120.0,
      "end_time": 138696.0,
      "text": "They own 90 percent of the e-commerce --"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 138720.0,
      "end_time": 140376.0,
      "text": "pretty much the whole market --"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 140400.0,
      "end_time": 142735.0,
      "text": "85 percent of social media,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 142759.0,
      "end_time": 145896.0,
      "text": "85 percent of internet payment."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 145920.0,
      "end_time": 152456.0,
      "text": "And they also own large volumes of digital content, video, online movie,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 152480.0,
      "end_time": 155640.0,
      "text": "literature, travel information, gaming."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 157200.0,
      "end_time": 160456.0,
      "text": "When this huge base of mobile shoppers"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 160480.0,
      "end_time": 162935.0,
      "text": "meets with aggregated ecosystems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 162960.0,
      "end_time": 164816.0,
      "text": "chemical reactions happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 164840.0,
      "end_time": 167456.0,
      "text": "Today, China is like a huge laboratory"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 167480.0,
      "end_time": 170296.0,
      "text": "generating all sorts of experiments."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 170320.0,
      "end_time": 171775.0,
      "text": "You should come to China,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 171800.0,
      "end_time": 175400.0,
      "text": "because here you will get a glimpse into the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 176520.0,
      "end_time": 180760.0,
      "text": "One of the trends I have seen concerns the spontaneity of shopping."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 181440.0,
      "end_time": 183496.0,
      "text": "Five years ago, in a fashion study,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 183520.0,
      "end_time": 184976.0,
      "text": "we found that on average,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 185000.0,
      "end_time": 188936.0,
      "text": "a Chinese consumer would be buying five to eight pairs of shoes."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 188960.0,
      "end_time": 193336.0,
      "text": "This number tripled to reach about 25 pairs of shoes a year."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 193360.0,
      "end_time": 195920.0,
      "text": "Who would need so many pairs of shoes?"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 196520.0,
      "end_time": 199656.0,
      "text": "So I asked them, \"What are the reasons you buy?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 199680.0,
      "end_time": 202336.0,
      "text": "They told me a list of inspirations:"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 202360.0,
      "end_time": 207160.0,
      "text": "blogs, celebrity news, fashion information."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 207400.0,
      "end_time": 210495.0,
      "text": "But really, for many of them, there was no particular reason to buy."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 210520.0,
      "end_time": 213160.0,
      "text": "They were just browsing on their mobile site"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 213400.0,
      "end_time": 215160.0,
      "text": "and then buying whatever they saw."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 216560.0,
      "end_time": 220816.0,
      "text": "We have observed the same level of spontaneity in everything,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 220840.0,
      "end_time": 224520.0,
      "text": "from grocery shopping to buying insurance products."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 226240.0,
      "end_time": 229816.0,
      "text": "But it is not very difficult to understand if you think about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 229840.0,
      "end_time": 232576.0,
      "text": "A lot of the Chinese consumers are still very new"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 232600.0,
      "end_time": 235816.0,
      "text": "in their middle-class or upper-middle-class lifestyles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 235840.0,
      "end_time": 238816.0,
      "text": "with a strong desire to buy everything new,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 238840.0,
      "end_time": 240896.0,
      "text": "new products, new services."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 240920.0,
      "end_time": 243616.0,
      "text": "And with this integrated ecosystem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 243640.0,
      "end_time": 248119.0,
      "text": "it is so easy for them to buy, one click after another."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 249520.0,
      "end_time": 254160.0,
      "text": "However, this new shopping behavior is creating a lot of challenges"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 254400.0,
      "end_time": 256776.0,
      "text": "for those once-dominant businesses."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 256800.0,
      "end_time": 260656.0,
      "text": "The owner of a fashion company told me that he&#39;s so frustrated"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 260680.0,
      "end_time": 264800.0,
      "text": "because his customers keep complaining that his products are not new enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 265320.0,
      "end_time": 268120.0,
      "text": "Well, for a fashion company, really bad comment."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 269519.0,
      "end_time": 272976.0,
      "text": "And he already increased the number of products in each collection."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 273000.0,
      "end_time": 274200.0,
      "text": "It doesn&#39;t seem to work."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 274800.0,
      "end_time": 278216.0,
      "text": "So I told him there&#39;s something more important than that."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 278240.0,
      "end_time": 281696.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ve got to give your consumer exactly what they want"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 281720.0,
      "end_time": 282960.0,
      "text": "when they still want it."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 283720.0,
      "end_time": 288256.0,
      "text": "And he can learn something from the online apparel players in China."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 288280.0,
      "end_time": 291535.0,
      "text": "These companies, they collect real consumer feedback"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 291560.0,
      "end_time": 294560.0,
      "text": "from mobile sites, from social media,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 294800.0,
      "end_time": 297376.0,
      "text": "and then their designers will translate this information"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 297400.0,
      "end_time": 299960.0,
      "text": "into product ideas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 299120.0,
      "end_time": 302600.0,
      "text": "and then send them to microstudios for production."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 303160.0,
      "end_time": 306976.0,
      "text": "These microstudios are really key in this overall ecosystem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 307000.0,
      "end_time": 309176.0,
      "text": "because they take small orders,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 309200.0,
      "end_time": 311376.0,
      "text": "30 garments at a time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 311400.0,
      "end_time": 314599.0,
      "text": "and they can also make partially customized pieces."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 315800.0,
      "end_time": 318976.0,
      "text": "The fact that all these production designs"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 319000.0,
      "end_time": 320456.0,
      "text": "are done locally,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 320480.0,
      "end_time": 325160.0,
      "text": "the whole process, from transporting to product on shelf or online"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 325400.0,
      "end_time": 327616.0,
      "text": "sometimes takes only three to four days."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 327640.0,
      "end_time": 329336.0,
      "text": "That is super fast,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 329360.0,
      "end_time": 332976.0,
      "text": "and that is highly responsive to what is in and hot on the market."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 333000.0,
      "end_time": 337296.0,
      "text": "And that is giving enormous headaches to traditional retailers"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 337320.0,
      "end_time": 340159.0,
      "text": "who are only thinking about a few collections a year."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 342280.0,
      "end_time": 345679.0,
      "text": "Then there&#39;s a consumer&#39;s need for ultraconvenience."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 346240.0,
      "end_time": 349456.0,
      "text": "A couple of months ago, I was shopping with a friend in Tokyo."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 349480.0,
      "end_time": 350736.0,
      "text": "We were in the store,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 350760.0,
      "end_time": 353575.0,
      "text": "and there were three to four people standing in front of us"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 353600.0,
      "end_time": 355560.0,
      "text": "at the checkout counter."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 355800.0,
      "end_time": 356616.0,
      "text": "Pretty normal, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 356640.0,
      "end_time": 359416.0,
      "text": "But both of us dropped our selection"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 359440.0,
      "end_time": 360640.0,
      "text": "and walked away."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 361440.0,
      "end_time": 363680.0,
      "text": "This is how impatient we have become."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 364560.0,
      "end_time": 368416.0,
      "text": "Delivering ultraconvenience is not just something nice to have."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 368440.0,
      "end_time": 371520.0,
      "text": "It is crucial to make sure your consumer actually buys."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 372360.0,
      "end_time": 374536.0,
      "text": "And in China, we have learned"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 374560.0,
      "end_time": 378696.0,
      "text": "that convenience is really the glue that will make online shopping"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 378720.0,
      "end_time": 381696.0,
      "text": "a behavior and a habit that sticks."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 381720.0,
      "end_time": 385296.0,
      "text": "It is sometimes more effective than a loyalty program alone."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 385320.0,
      "end_time": 387160.0,
      "text": "Take Hema."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 387400.0,
      "end_time": 391800.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a retail grocery concept developed by Alibaba."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 391600.0,
      "end_time": 393576.0,
      "text": "They deliver a full basket of products"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 393600.0,
      "end_time": 396856.0,
      "text": "from 4,000 SKUs to your doorstep"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 396880.0,
      "end_time": 398736.0,
      "text": "within 30 minutes."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 398760.0,
      "end_time": 402856.0,
      "text": "What is amazing is that they deliver literally everything:"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 402880.0,
      "end_time": 405960.0,
      "text": "fruits, vegetables, of course."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 405120.0,
      "end_time": 407456.0,
      "text": "They also deliver live fish"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 407480.0,
      "end_time": 409800.0,
      "text": "and also live Alaska king crab."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 410960.0,
      "end_time": 413215.0,
      "text": "Like my friend once told me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 413240.0,
      "end_time": 414936.0,
      "text": "\"It&#39;s really my dream coming true."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 414960.0,
      "end_time": 417895.0,
      "text": "Finally, I can impress my mother-in-law"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 417920.0,
      "end_time": 420896.0,
      "text": "when she comes to visit me for dinner unexpectedly.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 420920.0,
      "end_time": 424216.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 424240.0,
      "end_time": 426896.0,
      "text": "Well, companies like Amazon and FreshDirect"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 426920.0,
      "end_time": 429816.0,
      "text": "are also experimenting in the same field."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 429840.0,
      "end_time": 433416.0,
      "text": "The fact that Hema is part of the Alibaba ecosystem"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 433440.0,
      "end_time": 436960.0,
      "text": "makes it faster and also a bit easier to implement."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 437760.0,
      "end_time": 439656.0,
      "text": "For an online grocery player,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 439680.0,
      "end_time": 442496.0,
      "text": "it is very difficult, very costly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 442520.0,
      "end_time": 445296.0,
      "text": "to deliver a full basket quickly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 445320.0,
      "end_time": 447936.0,
      "text": "but for Hema, it&#39;s got a mobile app,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 447960.0,
      "end_time": 449616.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s got mobile payment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 449640.0,
      "end_time": 455336.0,
      "text": "and also it&#39;s built 20 physical stores in high-density areas in Shanghai."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 455360.0,
      "end_time": 459256.0,
      "text": "These stores are built to ensure the freshness of the product --"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 459280.0,
      "end_time": 462176.0,
      "text": "they actually have fish tanks in the store --"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 462200.0,
      "end_time": 466479.0,
      "text": "and also to give locations that will enable high-speed delivery."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 466920.0,
      "end_time": 468936.0,
      "text": "I know the question you have on your mind."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 468960.0,
      "end_time": 470215.0,
      "text": "Are they making money?"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 470240.0,
      "end_time": 471576.0,
      "text": "Yes, they are making money."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 471600.0,
      "end_time": 472856.0,
      "text": "They are breaking even,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 472880.0,
      "end_time": 476456.0,
      "text": "and what is also amazing is that the sales revenue per store"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 476480.0,
      "end_time": 480496.0,
      "text": "is three to four times higher than the traditional grocery store,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 480520.0,
      "end_time": 484159.0,
      "text": "and half of the revenue orders are coming from mobile."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 485400.0,
      "end_time": 487896.0,
      "text": "This is really proof that a consumer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 487920.0,
      "end_time": 491496.0,
      "text": "if you give them ultraconvenience that really works in grocery shopping,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 491520.0,
      "end_time": 494376.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re going to switch their shopping behaviors online,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 494400.0,
      "end_time": 495599.0,
      "text": "like, in no time."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 497480.0,
      "end_time": 500576.0,
      "text": "So ultraconvenience and spontaneity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 500600.0,
      "end_time": 502456.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s not the full story."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 502480.0,
      "end_time": 504616.0,
      "text": "The other trend I have seen in China"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 504640.0,
      "end_time": 505880.0,
      "text": "is social shopping."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 506440.0,
      "end_time": 509560.0,
      "text": "If you think of social shopping elsewhere in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 509800.0,
      "end_time": 510520.0,
      "text": "it is a linear process."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 511560.0,
      "end_time": 513696.0,
      "text": "You pick up something on Facebook,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 513720.0,
      "end_time": 516336.0,
      "text": "watch it, and you switch to Amazon"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 516360.0,
      "end_time": 519560.0,
      "text": "or brand.com to complete the shopping journey."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 519799.99999999994,
      "end_time": 520735.99999999994,
      "text": "Clean and simple."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 520760.0,
      "end_time": 523856.0,
      "text": "But in China it is a very different thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 523880.0,
      "end_time": 528616.0,
      "text": "On average, a consumer would spend one hour on their mobile phone shopping."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 528640.0,
      "end_time": 531295.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s three times higher than the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 531320.0,
      "end_time": 533256.0,
      "text": "Where does the stickiness come from?"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 533280.0,
      "end_time": 536680.0,
      "text": "What are they actually doing on this tiny little screen?"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 537120.0,
      "end_time": 539576.0,
      "text": "So let me take you on a mobile shopping journey"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 539600.0,
      "end_time": 541520.0,
      "text": "that I usually would be experiencing."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 543000.0,
      "end_time": 545960.0,
      "text": "11pm, yes, that&#39;s usually when I shop."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 546800.0,
      "end_time": 550415.0,
      "text": "I was having a chat in a WeChat chatroom with my friends."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 550440.0,
      "end_time": 552536.0,
      "text": "One of them took out a pack of snack"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 552560.0,
      "end_time": 555839.0,
      "text": "and posted the product link in that chatroom."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 556320.0,
      "end_time": 560160.0,
      "text": "I hate it, because usually I would just click that link"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 560400.0,
      "end_time": 562656.0,
      "text": "and then land on the product page."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 562680.0,
      "end_time": 564935.0,
      "text": "Lots of information, very colorful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 564960.0,
      "end_time": 566376.0,
      "text": "mind-blowing."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 566400.0,
      "end_time": 569136.0,
      "text": "Watched it and then a shop assistant came online"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 569160.0,
      "end_time": 572216.0,
      "text": "and asked me, \"How can I help you tonight?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 572240.0,
      "end_time": 574416.0,
      "text": "Of course I bought that pack of snack."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 574440.0,
      "end_time": 578496.0,
      "text": "What is more beautiful is I know that the next day, around noontime,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 578520.0,
      "end_time": 581376.0,
      "text": "that pack of snack will be delivered to my office."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 581400.0,
      "end_time": 584160.0,
      "text": "I can eat it and share it with my colleagues"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 584400.0,
      "end_time": 586920.0,
      "text": "and the cost of delivery, maximum one dollar."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 588240.0,
      "end_time": 591176.0,
      "text": "Just when I was about to leave that shopping site,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 591200.0,
      "end_time": 593560.0,
      "text": "another screen popped up."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 593800.0,
      "end_time": 597736.0,
      "text": "This time it is the livestreaming of a grassroots celebrity"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 597760.0,
      "end_time": 601160.0,
      "text": "teaching me how to wear a new color of lipstick."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 601400.0,
      "end_time": 604136.0,
      "text": "I watched for 30 seconds -- very easy to understand --"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 604160.0,
      "end_time": 607216.0,
      "text": "and also there is a shopping link right next to it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 607240.0,
      "end_time": 609880.0,
      "text": "clicked it, bought it in a few seconds."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 610600.0,
      "end_time": 612960.0,
      "text": "Back to the chatroom."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 612120.0,
      "end_time": 613976.0,
      "text": "The gossiping is still going on."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 614000.0,
      "end_time": 616856.0,
      "text": "Another friend of mine posted the QR code"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 616880.0,
      "end_time": 618536.0,
      "text": "of another pack of snack."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 618560.0,
      "end_time": 620790.0,
      "text": "Clicked it, bought it."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 621800.0,
      "end_time": 622656.0,
      "text": "So the whole experience"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 622680.0,
      "end_time": 626455.0,
      "text": "is like you&#39;re exploring in an amusement park."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 626480.0,
      "end_time": 629960.0,
      "text": "It is chaotic, it is fun"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 629120.0,
      "end_time": 631520.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s even a little bit addictive."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 632520.0,
      "end_time": 636936.0,
      "text": "This is what&#39;s happening when you have this integrated ecosystem."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 636960.0,
      "end_time": 639656.0,
      "text": "Shopping is embedded in social,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 639680.0,
      "end_time": 644376.0,
      "text": "and social is evolving into a multidimensional experience."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 644400.0,
      "end_time": 648960.0,
      "text": "The integration of ecosystems reaches a whole new level."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 648120.0,
      "end_time": 651440.0,
      "text": "So does its dominance in all aspects of our life."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 652720.0,
      "end_time": 656336.0,
      "text": "And of course, there are huge commercial opportunities behind it."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 656360.0,
      "end_time": 659176.0,
      "text": "A Chinese snack company, Three Squirrels,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 659200.0,
      "end_time": 662976.0,
      "text": "built a half-a-billion-dollar business in just three years"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 663000.0,
      "end_time": 666816.0,
      "text": "by investing in 300 to 500 shop assistants"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 666840.0,
      "end_time": 670976.0,
      "text": "who are going to be online to provide services 24/7."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 671000.0,
      "end_time": 673160.0,
      "text": "In the social media environment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 673400.0,
      "end_time": 674976.0,
      "text": "they are like your neighborhood friends."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 675000.0,
      "end_time": 676696.0,
      "text": "Even when you are not buying stuff,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 676720.0,
      "end_time": 680120.0,
      "text": "they will be happy to just tell you a few jokes and make you happy."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 681000.0,
      "end_time": 683960.0,
      "text": "In this integrated ecosystem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 683120.0,
      "end_time": 687576.0,
      "text": "social media can really redefine the relationship between brand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 687600.0,
      "end_time": 689600.0,
      "text": "retailer and consumer."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 691440.0,
      "end_time": 694896.0,
      "text": "These are only fragments of the massive changes"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 694920.0,
      "end_time": 696616.0,
      "text": "I have seen in China."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 696640.0,
      "end_time": 698616.0,
      "text": "In this huge laboratory,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 698640.0,
      "end_time": 702319.0,
      "text": "a lot of experiments are generated every single day."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 703400.0,
      "end_time": 705536.0,
      "text": "The ecosystems are reforming,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 705560.0,
      "end_time": 709736.0,
      "text": "supply chain distribution, marketing, product innovation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 709760.0,
      "end_time": 710976.0,
      "text": "everything."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 711000.0,
      "end_time": 715256.0,
      "text": "Consumers are getting the power to decide what they want to buy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 715280.0,
      "end_time": 716576.0,
      "text": "when they want to buy it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 716600.0,
      "end_time": 719616.0,
      "text": "how they want to buy it, how they want to social."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 719640.0,
      "end_time": 723560.0,
      "text": "It is now back to business leaders of the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 723800.0,
      "end_time": 726416.0,
      "text": "to really open their eyes, see what&#39;s happening in China,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 726440.0,
      "end_time": 729440.0,
      "text": "think about it and take actions."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 730320.0,
      "end_time": 731536.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 731560.0,
      "end_time": 734359.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 739760.0,
      "end_time": 742240.0,
      "text": "Massimo Portincaso: Angela,  what you shared with us"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 742260.0,
      "end_time": 744380.0,
      "text": "is truly impressive and almost incredible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 744400.0,
      "end_time": 749656.0,
      "text": "but I think many in the audience had the same question that I had,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 749680.0,
      "end_time": 750896.0,
      "text": "which is:"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 750920.0,
      "end_time": 754256.0,
      "text": "Is this kind of impulsive consumption"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 754280.0,
      "end_time": 758496.0,
      "text": "both economically and environmentally sustainable over the longer term?"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 758520.0,
      "end_time": 762256.0,
      "text": "And what is the total price to be paid"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 762280.0,
      "end_time": 766976.0,
      "text": "for such an automized and ultraconvenient retail experience?"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 767000.0,
      "end_time": 769896.0,
      "text": "Angela Wang: Yeah. One thing we have to keep in mind"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 769920.0,
      "end_time": 773640.0,
      "text": "is really, we are at the very beginning of a huge transformation."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 774200.0,
      "end_time": 777336.0,
      "text": "So with this trading up needs of the consumer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 777360.0,
      "end_time": 780496.0,
      "text": "together with the evolution of the ecosystem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 780520.0,
      "end_time": 784295.0,
      "text": "there are a lot of opportunities and also challenges."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 784320.0,
      "end_time": 785896.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;ve seen some early signs"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 785920.0,
      "end_time": 788776.0,
      "text": "that the ecosystems are shifting their focus"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 788800.0,
      "end_time": 791376.0,
      "text": "to pay attention to solve these challenges."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 791400.0,
      "end_time": 795656.0,
      "text": "For example, paying more consideration to sustainability"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 795680.0,
      "end_time": 797616.0,
      "text": "alongside just about speed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 797640.0,
      "end_time": 800496.0,
      "text": "and also quality over quantity."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 800520.0,
      "end_time": 803456.0,
      "text": "But there are really no simple answers to these questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 803480.0,
      "end_time": 806960.0,
      "text": "That is exactly why I&#39;m here to tell everyone"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 806120.0,
      "end_time": 811000.0,
      "text": "that we need to watch it, study it, and play a part in this evolution."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 811680.0,
      "end_time": 813215.0,
      "text": "MP: Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 813240.0,
      "end_time": 814456.0,
      "text": "AW: Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 814480.0,
      "end_time": 817120.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}